00:20:49.000 --> 00:20:56.000
So this code up here inside this function, this runs one time whenever the user initially loads the application,

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:58.000
whenever there's a new session.

00:20:58.000 --> 00:21:04.000
But this code in here inside the rendering function runs every time any of its inputs change.

00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:09.000
So any of the inputs that go into this render table function change, it'll rerun.

00:21:09.000 --> 00:21:12.000
So you want to try to, if something doesn't depend on those inputs,

00:21:12.000 --> 00:21:19.000
try to pull that logic outside of the function and have it be stored as a bit of state.

