00:24:39.000 --> 00:24:44.000
And if you're running into speed problems in an R app, you might switch to something like DuckDB or Arrow,

00:24:44.000 --> 00:24:47.000
which is a little bit better at handling large data sets faster.

00:24:47.000 --> 00:24:51.000
