00:32:15.000 --> 00:32:22.000
And this is a kind of core issue with a core principle of, I guess, reactivity,

00:32:22.000 --> 00:32:26.000
which is that with reactivity, you really don't want to repeat yourself.

00:32:26.000 --> 00:32:28.000
And there's two reasons for that.

00:32:28.000 --> 00:32:32.000
The first one is that you want to keep your code encapsulated in one place.

00:32:32.000 --> 00:32:37.000
